com.abstractdata.Interface

Interface StackADT<D>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MyStack

    public interface StackADT<D>
extends java.io.Serializable
    This is the Stack Interface for an Abstract Stack This Stack embodies all the standard Stack operations, and includes several helper methods that will give the data structure more flexibility and use.
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Matt Jones
